diag_norcpm is a diagnostic package to plot the output data from NorESM members.
    as a goal.

It contains a mainscript: diag_norcpm.sh
    which define the plot name and the directories of input data
    the receipt to do
    and directory to output plots.

A set of receipts: Receipts/
    contains the receipts
    receipt define the plot scripts to run and how to generate the plot script

A python script which do everything: doplot.py
    parse the receipts
    generate plot script which is assign in receipt
    run the plot script

A set of plot script: Codes/
    contain plot and proc script templates


flow chart
------------------
| diag_norcpm.sh |
|   plotCase     |
|   receipt(s)   |
|   input data   |
|   output dir   |
------------------
        |
        V
-------------------------------------
| doplot.py                         |
|   read and parse receipts         |
|   generate plot scripts in receipt|
|   (run scripts)                   |
-------------------------------------


How it work:
    Generate plot script is simply. doplot.py replace strings in plot script template.
    The strings to be replace are defined in receipt and plot script template(as default value).
    See Codes/gen_proc_plot.py

